metadata.name: Bare di Cristallo
metadata.description:
A re-imagination of the book cover for "Die Glasfalle", a novel by H. W. Franke.

Released on the occasion of the Tribute to Herbert W. Franke.  
100% of the net proceeds from the primary sale are donated to the Foundation Herbert W. Franke.

https://www.tribute-hwf.com/

Cristalli Series (215905460950833L), Generative artwork made with Processing.

3840 × 2160px

Prints and higher resolution files available upon request: prints@stefancontiero.com
